Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:19.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:25.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:31.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:37.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:43.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:49.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:58.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:18.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:37.06,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(118,142)}BROKEN HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:39.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy missiles closing in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're reading a metallic signature\Nat 1 o'clock, range 10 km!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:45.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A metallic signature?\NI wonder if it's the enemy base?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:46.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy missiles, twenty seconds to impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:53.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy missiles are closing in!\NSkull 5, 6, and 7, intercept at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:59.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Leader, we're reading a metallic\Nsignature at the missile launch site.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:02.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Input the data and attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:03.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:13.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's our turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:21.33,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,ATTACK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:34.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting any life signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like those missiles were\Nan automated attack system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:45.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The guys who were here must have\Nreally panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:54.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't have left more than\Ntwo or three hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayase here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:02.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, there's a large stash\Nof weapons in the arms depot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:05.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. Go ahead and block off\Nthe depot, just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our job just got easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't they just do something\Nreckless to get more weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:15.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Kamujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling of speed is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you bums keeping up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lap'Lamiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go even faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a good mood, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"In a good mood," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:43.04,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,You say I'm falling for him
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:41.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:48.09,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I love you more
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:53.93,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Always together on Sunset Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:04:00.47,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,A salt breeze blows, a big wave
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:03.87,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,He begins to occupy my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, we've got to get\Nout of here! Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:41.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:50.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Behave yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!\NWhat are you doing with Minmay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:03.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with you losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's get the hell out of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:23.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, old man Global.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:39.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:40.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:46.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who these two are, yes?\NKaifun and Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:54.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you value their lives, you will give me\Na warship by 0600 hours tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:02.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't? Then by six AM tomorrow,\Nthese two will be goners!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared ya, didn't I?\NServes you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You can't give these people a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Oh, be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If that ship is worth handing\Nover to them, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,just destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:23.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:29.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can do what he says\Nor what I say, it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:33.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:35.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:38.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and make sure it comes\Nfully equipped, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:41.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazin', Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:55.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking these two prisoner and\Ntrading 'em for a warship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:59.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just learned how to do\Nthings the Earth way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's up to the military now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:06.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all part of the plan,\Nbut I really can't stand waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see war and chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some stimulation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe in the meantime, you can be my toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:21.60,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Time drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:26.20,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,love drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:35.42,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing before me, a sad look on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:44.49,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're going off to war
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.79,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,All the men, toge...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:51.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you thought I'd do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:55.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not so unsophisticated that\Nyou can fool us like that anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Unsophisticated"?\NDid I hear that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:07:59.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised us with your songs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but that was back before we knew\Nthe first thing about culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?\NThat was all it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:12.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Did you really think your songs\Nhave the power to move people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd just never heard one before, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:23.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But those idiots got themselves\Nall riled up about culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You turned them into a bunch of cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The hostage!\NThe hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't dead, is she?\NI forgot she was our valuable hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:42.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lap'Lamiz.\NCut that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, but just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:47.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoopsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a "cultured" game, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:56.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Brigadier General Motokov?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:05.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Zentradi have never taken hostages and\Ndemanded anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:09.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. We humans have influenced\Nthem once again, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:13.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving those people a battleship\Nis completely unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:16.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We should launch an all-out strike to\Nprevent this from happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is that the hostages\Nare celebrities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:24.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we ignore this demand and they end up\Ngetting killed, the media...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our governmental authority still\Nisn't firmly established.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We must avoid agitating the public!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:36.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still plenty of time left\Nbefore 0600 tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:39.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we can come up with\Nan idea or two before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The 103rd Destroid Platoon\Nhas its garrison there,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:56.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,so it looks like this will be a joint operation,\Nand you'll be in command.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:02.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go over the mission details one more\Ntime and then start issuing orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, be careful. I'll be waiting\Nfor you with some rose tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:10.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me our escort, Captain Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:11.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Cheshire Cat.\NSkull Leader, please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Skull Leader.\NHave you found them, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our worst predictions have come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin's up to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:27.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taken hostages in lonesco City and is\Ndemanding a battleship for their return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't fool around, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And here we've spent all this\Ntime looking for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who are the hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two of them: Kaifun and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NIs Minmay okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as of right now, she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:48.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we're going to coordinate with\Na nearby Destroid platoon and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:50.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:51.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NYes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be a joint operation with another unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll inform you of the details later.\NUnderstood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah, for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:13.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I can't believe he\Ntook Minmay hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you really think Kamujin\Nwill fall for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already been over this a dozen times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:31.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kamujin we're talking about.\NHe'll fall for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:33.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if he doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:39.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd rather surround the city\Nand start attacking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,while I slip in and rescue the hostages?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That idea the top brass came up with has\Nno regard for the hostages' lives
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,so if that's the plan that gets used,\Nyou can count me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in command, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's a way that things are\Ndone in the field, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch that tone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been put in charge of this operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The lives of the hostages take top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure get worked up over\NMinmay, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be like this if I were the hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:10.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:14.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you joke around like that when\Npeoples' lives are at stake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:23.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Requesting instructions, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:26.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch Valkyrie squadron.\NHead for the rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroid platoon, stand by to scramble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lap'Lamiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll have another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good drinker.\NI like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:57.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:06.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.\NIt won't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how hard they\Nshoved those things in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think someone will help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:16.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I can't imagine the military\Njust handing over a battleship for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If this isn't handled right, we might\Nbe left to fend for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:20.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:24.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what it comes to,\Nwe don't have much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Hikaru will come save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:32.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's try talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not hopeless!\NThey're humans, just like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, you're\Nnothing but talk, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:45.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! What good will\Na battleship do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:49.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you start another war and cause\Nthe deaths of your brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:52.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,War accomplishes absolutely nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:56.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You all know the pointlessness of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But now you've come into contact\Nwith culture, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why throw away that culture?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to living your lives\Naccording to culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply obeying your destructive\Nimpulses is no kind of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Culture, culture!" You're one\Nannoying fool, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We know how to make culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Make culture"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:22.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NHey, Lap'Lamiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:27.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?\NThis is how you make culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, I'm sorry to interrupt while\Nyou're making culture...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:50.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But some of our guys are\Ncalling in and asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when the culture was getting good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pick up from there later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:02.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin! We heard you were in\Nlonesco City, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:04.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:06.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:09.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we came here hoping\Nyou'd let us join you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but we were spotted by a patrol unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us, Kamujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us, Kamuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:19.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help you.\NJust hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, men, we're heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to get rid of all that anger\Nwe've been keepin' in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so how was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I guess.\NHere, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:39.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's culture sure is tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking all these men?\NThat's almost all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:51.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cut out for waiting.\NNeither are they.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:54.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:57.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the culture will have to wait till later...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you take the Glauj.\NDo you want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:03.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:05.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't slow us down at all, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But what will you pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've got something good to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, men!\NLet's go save our comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a kick to the side means\N"move forward," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it mean "turn right"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:30.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter! If we don't get moving,\Nthe boss is gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Move forward, you stupid bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you it meant "advance," didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be easier if he just told us though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he wants to do like how\Nhe saw in that Western film.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:51.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The units in lonesco City have just moved out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:53.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:56.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,103rd Destroid Platoon, what's your status?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All green!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:06.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!\NIt's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they've done it!\NCrush them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:52.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin's forces and the Destroid Monsters\Nof the 103rd have commenced hostilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:54.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The mouse has fallen into the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:55.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:59.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only three Regulds around\Nyour target, the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.\NCommencing low-level run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, I'll get you out safely,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice... Is that you, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you choose such a\Ndangerous plan to rescue us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There must have been other options!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:17.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We took what we believed was\Nthe best course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:20.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We gave top priority to the\Nlives of the hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of hearing about your priorities!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You soldiers are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:30.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru and the others worked hard\Nto save us, Kaifun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:47.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...\NIt's been six months, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.23,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:02.48,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:06.47,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, you always shine so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:08.05,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:46.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!\NOut of ammo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of ammunition too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:55.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!\NI'm out of ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So try some of {\i1}this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lap'Lamiz!\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:08.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:17.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is it.\NWe're out of ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you bums!\NRetreat! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:29.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have Captain Ichijo help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:35.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:37.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. If he has time to hang all\Nover her, he's got time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:43.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Captain Ichijo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but Kamujin's men are on the run and\NI'd like you to help hunt them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've rescued the hostages,\Nisn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:52.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:55.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then ask someone else to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:05.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought you were a squadron commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:10.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine!\NYou want me to go, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:13.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:16.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It's been so long since\Nwe've seen each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NGive it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:23.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:28.33,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:34.58,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:41.51,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:41.27,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.16,0:22:43.03,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:49.05,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:49.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know I can return...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:52.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:55.03,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.51,0:23:02.78,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.39,0:23:10.46,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:19.50,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
